>;-)
>
> "My armour is like tenfold shields, my teeth are like swords,
> my claws spears, the shock of my tail a thunderbolt, my wings
> a hurricane, and my breath death."
>
> Tell me again how you solo'd Nagafen? <eg>
>
> Harmonic, the fisherman.

Bah! solo'ing Naga-pus is easy. Once my powerfist procs on em I just
fear/chain the old wyrm around his pitiful lair. Or if I am feeling lazy I
will charm a passing Guide/GM with my level 49 charm song and have them take
em out! Now let me tell ya how I solo'd all of the Plane of Sky in 28
mins....

Rokenn Swiftsong - Karana server
